channel.title: Problems with complier
channel.description:
if you are having problems with your complier right click it and click edit and see for this short part
[code]programfiles (x86) jdk1.6.0_30[/code] or somthing like that
look at the [code]programfiles(x86)[/code] might need to change to [code]programfiles[/code]
and also look at the [code]jdk1.6.0_30[/code] if you need to fix those errors
run it and it should work if it donsnt pm me so i can help
Thanks,king clay
P.S there are many other compiler code and i will list more later on
